      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPIRIT OF MARMYTE NZ (2) is a three-year-old filly by Lather Up from Spirit Of Art on debut. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Likely to attract plenty of interest from punters. HIGHWAY HUSTLER (1) was responsible for a very good effort last time over 1609m at Port Pirie, finishing second and just a nose from the winner. Sure to enjoy an economical run from this draw. Good enough to take out a race like this. SONNY RENNT (6) is in the mix at his first run since finishing fourth over 1660m at Victor Harbor four-and-a-half months ago. TWO STEP PROPOSAL (5) disappointed last time when ninth over 1800m at this track. Can do a lot better so worth considering.",
